{"tid":2075475,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全球反國安法｜歐盟：若強推國安法 將有負面後果","createTime":"2020-06-23T01:14:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T01:14:58.000Z","uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ef6078e6cd6150755ae62646d23716d4ca12f650","tid":2075475,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T01:14:58.000Z","msg":"歐盟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【🇪🇺全球反國安法｜歐盟：若強推國安法 將有負面後果】<br />\n<br />\n繼G7峰會聯合聲明後，歐盟再有動作。歐中領導人岩岩進行視像會議，歐洲理事會主席米歇爾會後表示，已經向中方表示歐盟嚴重關注國安法，呼籲北京遵守承諾，維持香港高度自治及保障自由，確保香港的政治多元、民主及人權水平。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟委員會主席馮德萊恩就話，國安法違反北京對國際的承諾，嚴重損害「一國兩制」原則及高度自治，一旦堅持立法，將有非常負面的後果，期望北京當局三思。<br />\n<br />\n今次見到歐盟立場漸漸硬起來，大家出力推下，等有再具體措施出爐。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/eucopresident/status/1275091982583504896\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Feucopresident%2Fstatus%2F1275091982583504896&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7gRUsGYs0X8VP9vM6mjQjJM%3D&h=74d4bddf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Feucopresident%2Fstatus%2F1275091982583504896&h=e0aab1e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/eucopresident/status/1275091982583504896</a><br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n【留一口氣，點一盞燈】眾志應急資金籌募：<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/香港眾志應急資金籌募/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E6%87%89%E6%80%A5%E8%B3%87%E9%87%91%E7%B1%8C%E5%8B%9F%2F&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7gRUsGYs0X8VP9vM6mjQjJM%3D&h=fa2e7287\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/香港眾志應急資金籌募/</a><br />\n反國安法街站要人： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/AntiNSLVolunteer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FAntiNSLVolunteer&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7gRUsGYs0X8VP9vM6mjQjJM%3D&h=86cb6807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blan